{"title":"川行诗抄","authors":["徐放"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":1,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"川行诗抄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访李白故里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在陇西院——一间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘着书香的老屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起“铁杵磨针”的故事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默立在你的衣冠塚前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我暗暗呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那书剑飘零"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄豪迈的诗魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，面对重重巴山，漫漫蜀道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不禁对天发问："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从古以来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这人间世，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行走在坎坷道路上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么多是诗人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重过三台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在三台县的史志上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝固了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们青年时代的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风怀和脚踪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁说，人的一生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰好似"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足踏雪泥的飞鸿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对灿烂的夕阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我满怀激情在想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要在晚年的岁月里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还能够发一点剩余的热和光的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的，又何必计较——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或得或失"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或升或沉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或枯或荣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早在青少年，我并不怀有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李白跋涉巴山蜀道时的感情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过几十年风雨飘泊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才体味到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生的旅途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该比巴山蜀道还要艰辛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这春天的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都结束了那段坎坷的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管不少往事使人伤心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我仍然要说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不用眼泪同你们告别，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们也不应该用眼泪为我送行！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}